    <div align="left" id="post_message_489372"><div align="center" style="margin:5px; margin-top:5px; ">
<table width="85%" border="0" align="center" cellpadding="5" cellspacing="0" bgcolor="#333333" class="bbcodeQUOTE">
  
    <td width="30" align="center" valign="middle"><img src="/forums/images/openq.gif" width="30" height="30" ></td>
    <td>
		<div align="left" style="font-size: 12px; color: #999999; font-family: Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;">As for there being a signification portion of gamers out there that don't care, that's horseshit and you know it. Those are two of the major reasons why PC gaming is miles ahead of console gaming and why people stick to it.</div>
