		<div align="left" style="font-size: 12px; color: #999999; font-family: Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;">CoD6 on the PC should be the same cost as the consoles. Afterall, it's the same game.<br />
What I mean is, since the developers can both harmonize the development process (only having to make one online system for the game instead of multiple for each console and the PC), it could decrease overall costs and drop game prices. It probably won't, but one can only hope.</div>
